00:23.678 --> 00:26.095
Fish don't fry
in the kitchen

00:26.233 --> 00:28.787
Beans don't burn
on the grill

00:28.925 --> 00:31.341
Took a whole lot of tryin'

00:31.479 --> 00:34.103
Just to get up that hill

00:34.241 --> 00:36.622
Now we're up
in the big leagues

00:36.760 --> 00:39.211
Gettin' our turn at bat

00:39.349 --> 00:41.696
As long as we live,
it's you and me, baby

00:41.834 --> 00:43.422
There ain't nothin' wrong
with that

